    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! It truly breaks my heart to even think about parting with this absolute gem, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the joy of driving a car that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014the paint is like a mirror and that interior still has that wonderful new-car scent. She\u2019s been garage-kept and loved, and honestly, you won't find another one this clean in the neighborhood. Come take a look and fall in love just like I did!",
      "price": 46500.0,
