    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine example of the high-revving S65 V8 masterpiece. This E92 M3 has been curated for the true purist, featuring VAC-coated rod bearings and a fully reinforced rear subframe to eliminate the platform's known structural harmonics. The induction note is sharpened by a carbon plenum, while the DCT logic has been recalibrated with GTS-spec software for near-instantaneous gear engagement. Every bushing has been inspected for compliance, and the suspension geometry is dialed for maximum lateral load without compromising high-speed stability. The finish is immaculate, reflecting a life spent in climate-controlled storage and a strict adherence to operating temperature protocols before any high-load demand. This is a turn-key, apex-ready machine with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 49250.0,
